snippet.title: LONDON FIELDS Official Trailer (2018) | Amber Heard * Thriller Mystery Movie*
snippet.description:
Kerala known as God's Own Country (In India - Southern India)  is facing severe crisis situation now. Almost 3/4th of the state is facing severe flood now. 32 Dams are overflooing heavily, and rain is not stopped yet. Hundreds of people died. Lakhs of people lost their houses. Damages may cause more than 5000 crores indian rupees (more than 80crore USD) . We need immense help. Please help us, please help us, please help us................... 

Help rebuild the lives of the flood affected people in Kerala

You can make donations online to Chief Ministers Disaster Relief Fund through

https://donation.cmdrf.kerala.gov.in 

This website may be inaccessible due to flood issues in the datacentre. If so, please see the bank account details to transfer the fund.

Name of Donee : Chief Ministers Disaster relief Fund
Account Number : 67319948232
Bank : State Bank Of India
Branch : City Branch , Trivandrum (Thiruvananthapuram)
IFSC : SBIN0070028
PAN: AAAGD0584M
Account Type : Savings
Swift Code : SBININBBT08


refer news here
